snippet.textDisplay: Believe in Jesus Believe who He say He is or what the Bible says He Is and Rely on Jesus as your Savior for He died for Your sins, so Rely on Him as Your Savior and your Forgiveness of Sins for we are Sinners. All of us are Going to Hell because of our Sins 1 sin can get you to Hell for Eternity, But God was Merciful and Gave His only Begotten son to die for our Sins on a Cross He was flogged, hit, spit upon and put on a crown of Thorn crushed in His skull and have to carry a Cross and was Crucified on it He had nails on His hands and Feet and God poured out His wrath on Jesus killing His own Son for our Sins. So if we Believe and Rely on Him we can Be Saved and spend Eternity in With Christ and God forever and Ever. And Have Joy in our Lives, Good days and Bad days. God and Jesus Loves us even how bad, wicked, cruel, sinful we are. And He is coming Back, Jesus is going to come back He is coming soon. Give your Life to Him and Receive Him as your Lord and Savior, Repent from your sins and ask for Forgiveness from God.Rely on Jesus as for your Forgiveness of Sins. Believe in Jesus Believe who He say He is or what the Bible says He Is and Rely on Jesus Trust Him. ❤️❤️❤️❤️🙏
